<font color="yellow">[Episode 03]</font>

41
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,410
<font color="yellow">Benar, kau.</font>

42
00:02:57,510 --> 00:03:00,510
<font color="yellow">Yu Na-ku, kau yang membawanya ke atap.</font>

43
00:03:02,170 --> 00:03:04,610
<font color="yellow">Ah, halo.</font>

44
00:03:05,410 --> 00:03:06,540
<font color="yellow">Anda pasti ibunya Yu Na.</font>

45
00:03:07,510 --> 00:03:10,470
<font color="yellow">Kita bertemu sebelumnya saat saya sedang melakukan
pekerjaan sukarelawan.</font>

46
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:13,540
<font color="yellow">Apa... terjadi sesuatu pada Yu Na?</font>

47
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:16,410
<font color="yellow">Jangan pura-pura tak tahu apapun.</font>

48
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:19,670
<font color="yellow">Yu Na-ku kau dorong dari atap!</font>

49
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:26,140
<font color="yellow">Siapa kau?</font>

50
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:28,070
<font color="yellow">Ada apa ini?</font>

51
00:03:32,970 --> 00:03:35,070
<font color="yellow">Kantor Polisi Metropolitan Seoul, Jo Soo Ji.</font>

52
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:37,870
<font color="yellow">Putera Nyonya ditahan atas tuduhan...</font>

53
00:03:40,010 --> 00:03:42,270
<font color="yellow">...tindakan mencelakakan anak usia 7 tahun.</font>

54
00:03:43,410 --> 00:03:44,840
<font color="yellow">Itu mustahil.</font>

55
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:49,440
<font color="yellow">Ini foto mereka naik ke gedung itu bersama.</font>

56
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:52,470
<font color="yellow">Nyonya tidak mengenali wajah, pakaian, serta tas...</font>

57
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,770
<font color="yellow">...yang dikenakannya?</font>

58
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:59,740
<font color="yellow">Yu Na... jatuh dari atap?</font>

59
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:04,570
<font color="yellow">Yu Na baik-baik saja?
Dia tidak terluka parah, 'kan?</font>

60
00:04:08,970 --> 00:04:12,540
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak bisa menuduh puteraku hanya dengan sebuah foto kabur begitu.</font>

61
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:17,570
<font color="yellow">Tapi, Anda mengenali dia di foto ini.</font>

62
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,470
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak mau mengatakan apa-apa.</font>

63
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:24,110
<font color="yellow">Jika kau ingin menginvestigasinya,
bawa surat perintah resmi.</font>

64
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:27,440
<font color="yellow">Ya, akan kami bawakan.</font>

65
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:31,010
<font color="yellow">Kejaksaan Seoul, Kim Eun Joong Geomsa.</font>

66
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:33,510
<font color="yellow">Jika kalian tidak merespon permintaan investigasi kami,</font>

67
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,370
<font color="yellow">kami akan membawakan surat penahanan resmi.</font>

68
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:40,510
<font color="yellow">Ayah anakku... biar aku diskusi dulu dengan dia.</font>

69
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:44,810
<font color="yellow">Jika kau dari Kejaksaan Seoul,</font>

70
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,740
<font color="yellow">Geomsajang Yoon Seung Ro, kau pasti mengenalnya.</font>

71
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:50,440
<font color="yellow">Kau bisa terlambat. Ayo pergi.</font>

72
00:04:52,910 --> 00:04:54,370
<font color="yellow">Dia orangnya.</font>

73
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:56,910
<font color="yellow">Kau yakin?</font>

74
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:02,440
<font color="yellow">Ada stiker menempel padanya.
Yu Na yang tempel.</font>

75
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:06,240
<font color="yellow">Tapi beraninya dia berbohong mengatakan tak tahu apa-apa.</font>

76
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:10,370
<font color="yellow">Tenanglah. Kita harus menemukan bukti dulu.</font>

77
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:12,780
<font color="yellow">Jika tidak, kasusnya tidak akan berprogres.</font>

78
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:15,170
<font color="yellow">Aku akan menemukannya.</font>

79
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,140
<font color="yellow">Apa pun itu,</font>

80
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
<font color="yellow">aku pasti akan menemukannya,</font>

81
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,070
<font color="yellow">lalu menahan dia.</font>

82
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:31,270
<font color="yellow">Kim Geomsa.</font>

83
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:38,810
<font color="yellow">[Saksi Dicari]</font>

84
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:42,310
<font color="yellow">- Oh.
- Sedang apa kau di ruanganku?</font>

85
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:45,140
<font color="yellow">Aigoo, tentu menunggumu.
Ayo pergi makan bersama.</font>

86
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,010
<font color="yellow">Makan saja sendiri.</font>

87
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:52,970
<font color="yellow">Gimbap lagi?
Kenapa kau hidup begini? Kau bukannya orang miskin.</font>

88
00:05:53,210 --> 00:05:56,770
<font color="yellow">Ayahmu seorang Ketua Mahkamah Agung.
Jenjang karirmu itu bagus.</font>

89
00:05:56,940 --> 00:05:59,440
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau bekerja keras dan menghalangi jalanku?</font>

90
00:05:59,610 --> 00:06:01,640
<font color="yellow">Ayo keluar. Kutraktir, deh.</font>

91
00:06:03,570 --> 00:06:04,640
<font color="yellow">Lupakan saja.</font>

92
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:09,570
<font color="yellow">Pajak dari rakyat digunakan membayar gaji kita.
Selain bekerja, apalagi yang harus kita lakukan?</font>

93
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:12,070
<font color="yellow">Kerja saja dengan baik...</font>

94
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:15,070
<font color="yellow">...daripada sibuk mendekati para petinggi.</font>

95
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:19,940
<font color="yellow">Aku kemari juga untuk kerja.
Ingin tanya sesuatu padamu.</font>

96
00:06:20,570 --> 00:06:22,310
<font color="yellow">Tapi, kau sudah menemukan anak ini?</font>

97
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:24,810
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau peduli soal itu?</font>

98
00:06:24,810 --> 00:06:27,910
<font color="yellow">Anu, aku hanya mencemaskan Detektif Jo.</font>

99
00:06:28,110 --> 00:06:31,610
<font color="yellow">Kasus kecelakaan puterinya akan mempengaruhi kasus
Kim Woo Sung tidak?</font>

100
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:36,040
<font color="yellow">Kedengarannya, kau berharap ada dampaknya.</font>

101
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,170
<font color="yellow">Kau sudah salah paham.</font>

102
00:06:38,410 --> 00:06:40,210
<font color="yellow">Jadi, ketemu?</font>

103
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:42,410
<font color="yellow">Bukan urusanmu. Minggat sana!</font>

104
00:06:43,770 --> 00:06:47,040
<font color="yellow">Belakangan kau jadi semakin dingin saja.</font>

105
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:51,410
<font color="yellow">Hei, aku bahkan malas bicara denganmu.
Pergi saja... aish... sial!</font>

106
00:06:51,410 --> 00:06:53,170
<font color="yellow">Hei, maaf.
Aku ambilkan.</font>

107
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:55,740
<font color="yellow">Hei... hei... keluar saja sana!</font>

108
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:58,110
<font color="yellow">Mana mungkin aku pergi?</font>

109
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:01,010
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau menulis nama Geomsajangnim dan puteranya?</font>

110
00:07:01,010 --> 00:07:02,340
<font color="yellow">Meramal keberuntungan mereka?</font>

111
00:07:02,370 --> 00:07:04,170
<font color="yellow">Itu sama sekali bukan urusanmu!</font>

112
00:07:04,410 --> 00:07:07,270
<font color="yellow">Jangan mengamuk begitu.
Kau mencurigakan sekali.</font>

113
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:10,510
<font color="yellow">- Jangan-jangan...
- Tulis novel saja sana di rumah!</font>

114
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:13,110
<font color="yellow">Inilah sebabnya aku menyukaimu.</font>

115
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:16,370
<font color="yellow">Kau itu transparan, jadi terlihat jelas semuanya.</font>

116
00:07:16,470 --> 00:07:19,110
<font color="yellow">- Jangan kurang ajar!
- Tapi, kenapa kau tersipu begitu?</font>

117
00:07:19,110 --> 00:07:20,970
<font color="yellow">Aku... atau kasus ini?</font>

118
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:23,070
<font color="yellow">Aku ini sedang marah, tahu!</font>

119
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,470
<font color="yellow">Berhentilah menguji kesabaran orang lain.</font>

120
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:28,310
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak akan dapat apa-apa dariku!</font>

121
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:31,470
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu, aku akan lakukan langkah terakhir.</font>

122
00:07:33,710 --> 00:07:35,970
<font color="yellow">Geomsajangnim...
aku akan tanya langsung saja padanya.</font>

123
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:37,670
<font color="yellow">Lalu selanjutnya apa?</font>

124
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:39,270
<font color="yellow">Entahlah.</font>

125
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:49,740
<font color="yellow">Geomsajangnim tidak bisa mengambil alih kasus puteranya sendiri,</font>

126
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:51,810
<font color="yellow">tapi kita bisa melakukan untuknya.</font>

127
00:07:51,810 --> 00:07:54,210
<font color="yellow">Bujangnim, Anda mungkin tidak bisa membebaskan Kim Woo Sung,</font>

128
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:56,910
<font color="yellow">tapi Geomsajangnim pasti bisa.</font>

129
00:07:57,140 --> 00:08:00,370
<font color="yellow">Sekarang ini, kau mengajakku bernegosiasi?</font>

130
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:04,210
<font color="yellow">Tidak, bukan negosiasi.
Itu hanya... hanya...</font>

131
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:07,370
<font color="yellow">...saling memijat punggung masing-masing (saling membantu).</font>

132
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:12,610
<font color="yellow">Ada seorang jaksa di bawah kepemimpinan saya yang
dapat diandalkan.</font>

133
00:08:12,970 --> 00:08:15,040
<font color="yellow">Kami bisa mengurus segalanya untuk Anda.</font>

134
00:08:17,010 --> 00:08:20,870
<font color="yellow">Masyarakat selalu mengkritik kejaksaan terlalu politis,</font>

135
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:22,510
<font color="yellow">serta menyelidiki asal-asalan.</font>

136
00:08:23,570 --> 00:08:25,970
<font color="yellow">Anggap kasus putera Anda pun begitu, lalu...</font>

137
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:29,410
<font color="yellow">Kita selesaikan ini sebelum menjadi tidak terkendali.</font>

138
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:32,670
<font color="yellow">Itu terbaik untuk Geomsajangnim,
juga kejaksaan ini.</font>

139
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:40,540
<font color="yellow">Masalahmu itu, aku merasa risau sekali.</font>

140
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:43,440
<font color="yellow">Kau memenjarakan seorang pria tak berdosa,</font>

141
00:08:44,170 --> 00:08:48,340
<font color="yellow">dan menghancurkan citra kejaksaan kita.
Lalu, sekarang kau berani bicara ini demi kebaikan kita semua?</font>

142
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:59,540
<font color="yellow">Aku pikir kau hanya tak tahu malu,
rupanya kesadaran saja tak punya.</font>

143
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:03,070
<font color="yellow">- Maafkan saya.
- Jangan minta maaf.</font>

144
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:07,610
<font color="yellow">Dunia memang dipenuhi orang-orang sepertimu.</font>

145
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:28,140
<font color="yellow">Seorang jaksa yang memanfaatkan situasi krisis orang lain...</font>

146
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,470
<font color="yellow">...dan demonstran yang ingin menggulingkan pemerintahan...</font>

147
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:33,670
<font color="yellow">...karena akarnya, Sang Presiden, pun korupsi.</font>

148
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:39,310
<font color="yellow">Kalian semua bodoh...</font>

149
00:09:39,410 --> 00:09:42,710
<font color="yellow">...dan tidak bisa melihat sesuatu dengan benar.</font>

150
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,610
<font color="yellow">Bukankah kau bilang seorang anak jatuh dari atap?</font>

151
00:09:50,970 --> 00:09:52,040
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

152
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,970
<font color="yellow">Stabilitas organisasi kita,</font>

153
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:57,210
<font color="yellow">tidak boleh goyah karena seorang anak sepertinya.</font>

154
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:00,710
<font color="yellow">Orishin benar sekali.</font>

155
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:03,340
<font color="yellow">Buktikan padaku.</font>

156
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:06,410
<font color="yellow">Alasan kau harus kupertahankan.</font>

157
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:12,740
<font color="yellow">Jangan kuatir.
Saya akan pastikan kasus putera Anda selesai dengan tenang.</font>

158
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:36,910
<font color="yellow">[10 Mei 2016]</font>

159
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:42,940
<font color="yellow">Yu Na-ya.</font>

160
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,770
<font color="yellow">Eomma dan Halmeoni di sini.</font>

161
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:49,970
<font color="yellow">Kau masih ingin tidur saja?</font>

162
00:10:53,810 --> 00:10:58,040
<font color="yellow">Karena Eomma tidak memenuhi janji, kau masih marah.</font>

163
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:03,110
<font color="yellow">Tunggu sebentar, ya.</font>

164
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:06,610
<font color="yellow">Eomma akan menangkap pelakunya...</font>

165
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:10,610
<font color="yellow">...dan memastikan dia mendapat hukuman.</font>

166
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:15,170
<font color="yellow">Yu Na-ku harus bagun setelahnya, oke?</font>

167
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:21,740
<font color="yellow">Cucuku ini anak baik.
Kau pasti akan memenuhi keinginan ibumu, 'kan?</font>

168
00:11:23,070 --> 00:11:24,410
<font color="yellow">Eomma...</font>

169
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,040
<font color="yellow">- Silakan tunggu di luar.
- Astaga.</font>

170
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:35,140
<font color="yellow">Beri suntikan hipertensi dan bawa tas ambu kemari.</font>

171
00:11:50,110 --> 00:11:51,270
<font color="yellow">Anda ibunya?</font>

172
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,470
<font color="yellow">Kondisinya sudah stabil kembali.</font>

173
00:11:54,470 --> 00:11:57,110
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih. Terima kasih.</font>

174
00:11:57,770 --> 00:11:59,370
<font color="yellow">Artinya, dia baik-baik saja sekarang?</font>

175
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:04,440
<font color="yellow">Ah, dia masih belum sadarkan diri,
jadi hal seperti ini masih bisa terjadi.</font>

176
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,510
<font color="yellow">Kita tunggu dulu ia memenangkan pertarungannya (untuk membuka mata).</font>

177
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,840
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

178
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:17,970
<font color="yellow">- Aku pergi dulu.
